item.title: Model help and others like class 8
item.dc:creator: @Teh_Moose Teh Moose
item.description:
@Teh_Moose wrote:

You can’t put the classes into your server, the items are all added on the client side, so you’d need to download your own client and add them in there, then if people wanted to use the items on your server they’s either need to download your client or you would need to ceate a webclient.
